BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 625 Td ('I'm not going to say that,' Marcus said. 'It's not true and) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 610 Td (it could really hurt him.') Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 580 Td (Some kids laughed at Marcus. But by the end of the day, the kid) Tj ET
