BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 550 Td (for standing up for me.') Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 520 Td (That night, Marcus felt PEACE. The belt of truth kept him) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 505 Td (standing when it would have been easier to go along with the lie.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 475 Td (TRUTH holds your life together - just like a belt holds) Tj ET
