BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 655 Td (Her dad told her about the SHIELD OF FAITH.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 640 Td ('When scary thoughts come,' he said, 'they're like flaming) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 625 Td (arrows. Your faith is a shield that blocks them.') Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 595 Td (That night when the fear came, Emma whispered:) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 580 Td ('God is with me. God is bigger than anything in the dark.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 565 Td (I trust Him.' She imagined holding up a giant shield.) Tj ET
