BT 0.1 g /F2 14 Tf 191.76 730 Td (THE STORY: THE HELMET OF SALVATION) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 120 725 m 492 725 l S Q
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 700 Td (Jake used to think God could never love someone like him.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 685 Td (He'd messed up too many times. The voice in his head said:) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 670 Td ('You're too bad for God. Give up.') Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 640 Td (But then his youth leader explained SALVATION:) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 625 Td ('God already knows everything you've done. And He STILL) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 610 Td (chose to save you. You can't lose His love.') Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 580 Td (It was like putting on a helmet that blocked all the lies.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 550 Td ('But what about when I mess up again?' Jake asked.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 520 Td ('That's what grace is for. The helmet stays on.') Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 490 Td (The helmet of SALVATION protects your thoughts from the) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 10 Tf 72 475 Td (lie that you're not good enough for God!) Tj ET

endstream
